A man comes to the post office to send a parcel. There is not a single person in the hall, and the receptionist is reading a newspaper. The man turns to her:
- I would like ...
the receptionist interrupted:
- Man, get in line!
He continues to read the newspaper. Man to her:
- I'm sorry, but here...
the receptionist is again:
- Man, do I speak another language? Get in line!
And reads the newspaper on. The man got angry and spat in her face. Receptionist:
- What are you calling yourself? I'm going to call the police!
Guy:
- What makes you think it's me? Look at the queue here!
